  /As a user playing the game I want to:/

	  start the game by pressing a Start button
  ✔️use my arrow keys to change the direction of the snake
	✔️have the snake grow correctly when it eats the apple
	✔️have the game end if the snake tries to eat itself
	✔️have the game end if the snake runs into a wall
	✔️see how long my snake was when the game ended
	✔️start the game over without having to reset the browser

